author: dkulp
msg: More fixes for IBM JDK, unit tests fixes
* Fix type_test_wsdl.xsl to work with the IBM jdk
* Update top level pom to add a profile for IBM jdk to turn off -Xlint (it doesn't support SuppressWarnings)
* Fix WSDLToJavaProcessor to cleanup after itself.

* Change SchemaValidator to make sure the XMLSchema and wsdl schemas are first in the list to avoid problems parsing the other schemas.   This is kind of a hack.  There should be a ResourceResolver registered to handle much of those problems.
